 { q: 'Which polo is best for Vegas summer service techs?', a: 'Port Authority K540 Performance Silk Touch (moisture-wicking poly version of the K500) or Sport-Tek ST650 (budget alternative with comparable wicking). 100% cotton polos soak through by 11 AM in July. Performance fabrics keep wicking even after multiple service calls. Both take embroidery cleanly.' },
